SteamSale
  Ruby script for sale infomation on Steam Store.

/* REQUIREMENT */
  ruby v1.8.7~
  rubygem
  hpricot

/* USAGE */
  url.txt must be placed in data/ directory as default.

    $ruby main.rb

  Output:

   <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/***/" target="_blank">Game Title</a> $x.xx -> $y.yy (zz%off) 

/* SUPPORT */
